OL,5, The business secretary has said the    
OL,6, energy regulator allowed itself to have
OL,7, "the wool pulled over their eyes" over 
OL,8, prepayment meters being force-fitted.  
OL,10,FGrant Shapps accused Ofgem of taking   
OL,11,Fthe energy companies "at face value"   
OL,12,Finstead of listening to customers.     
OL,14,FLast week, the Times revealed an agency
OL,15,Fworking for British Gas was breaking   
OL,16,Finto vulnerable people's homes to fit  
OL,17,Fmeters that require advance payment.   
OL,19,FOfgem said it shared Mr Shapps' shock  
OL,20,Fat that report.                        
